snippet.title: Trailer for Pikmin 3.5
snippet.description:
This is the trailer that was shown in this years Pikmin direct, I’m so honoured that I was chosen to present the mod on the direct, a demo will be released shortly, please feel free to join my discord for more info ok the mod!

https://discord.gg/WBQxrmMvjH

(Do keep in mind that the mod had changed heavily since this trailer so it’s kinda outdated but’s whatever)
